<exploration xml:id="warm-queSabesSobre-lasPulgadas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ul>
      <li>They are used to measure length.</li>
      <li>There are inch marks on rulers, yardsticks, and tape measures.</li>
      <li>They are shorter than feet.</li>
      <li>They are longer than centimeters.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


